videos.headline: Guice, LSU rout Missouri to win Orgeron's debut
videos.description: Filling in for Leonard Fournette, Derrius Guice rushes for 163 yards and three touchdowns as LSU wins Ed Orgeron's debut as head coach with a 42-7 victory over Missouri.
